        <p>Isfrom pehle 2020 mein hi <strong>Harvard University of study</strong> ne mechanism samjhaaya — stress sympathetic nervous system ko activate karta hai jo melanocyte stem cells ko deplete karta hai. Lekin agar stress short-term tha and stem cells puri tarah khatam nahi hui hain, toh recovery possible hai.</p>

        <p><strong>Practical matlab:</strong> Agar aapke hair ofsi major stressful event (job loss, divorce, exam pressure, COVID illness) ke baad suddenly grey hue hain, toh stress management from reversal of chances achhi hain. Meditation, exercifrom, therapy, adequate sleep — yeh sab melanocyte recovery mein help karte hain.</p>

