        <p>Yeh sabfrom common and treatable reason hai premature greying ka. <a href="which-vitamin-deficiency-causes-white-hair.php">Kaun si vitamin deficiency from causes white hair</a> — yeh jaanna bahut zaroori hai.</p>

        <p><strong>Vitamin B12 Deficiency:</strong> B12 melanin production ke liye essential hai. India mein vegetarian diet common hone of wajah from B12 deficiency bahut prevalent hai. Studies show of B12 supplementation from premature greying partially reverfrom ho sakta hai — especially jab deficiency early stage mein detect ho.</p>

